}}</ref>. Deg kra n tikwal, kra n telmas n Malaṛya d tdefrin tinazbayin ssuturent isafaren niden yemgaraden. Akken i yettusemres deg kra n tikwal i wsuji n waṭṭan n [[ambyasis]] id yettilin deg beṛṛa n [[adan|wadan]] d [[azuwerzellim|uzuwerzellim]] d [[tamuccent (aṭṭan)|tmuccent]]. Asafar-a yettwasew s y[[imi]]

[[Asemdu amezlagu|isemda imezluga]] imezdiyen gan d uguren deg [[tamaẓwalt|tmaẓwalin]] d [[tunɣayt]] d uberriṭ ([[tadist (aṭṭan)|tadist]]).<ref name="AHFS2015" />. Ma d isemda imezluga imihanen gan d uguren deg usekkud d uttwiɣi n tmaẓwalin d [[tazɣint n tegrint|tezɣint n tegrint]] d [[uzuf aplastin|wuzuf aplestin]]. Macc yettuɣil d akken asafar-a d aneɣlis deg tallit n [[tadist]].<ref name="Preg2019">{{amnir n web
